mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "Square Dance Date Book", "From the Floor", "As I See It, by Bob Osgood", "Style Series: The Do Si Do", "Americana: The Arkansas Traveller, by Terry Golden", "Round Dancing: History, Part II by Kay and Forrest Richards", "Paging the Roundancers: Ross and Mable Hatton", "The Caller of the Month: Ruy Camp", "'Round the Outside Ring", "Workshop", "Handbook-Planning Square Dance Party Fun by Becky Osgood", "On the Record and Record Report", and "Experimental Lab: Stack the Wheel".
